data.title: Astrology Birth Chart for Dorothy Appleby (Jan. 6, 1906)
data.meta_description: Liz has two passions in life: astrology and relationships. As a professional astrologer, she has been featured in multiple publications such as BestLife, FoxNews, Glam, Glamour, and MindBodyGreen. She shares all her discoveries and observations on this website.
data.text:
Dorothy Appleby was an American film actress. She appeared in over 50 films from 1931 to 1943.

Dorothy Appleby was born on January 6, 1906, in Maine, Wisconsin, United States. Her birth geographical coordinates are 45° 1’ 38” North latitude and 89° 41’ 25” West longitude, with an altitude of 430 meters above sea level. Dorothy Appleby passed away at the age of 84 in 1990.

Astrologically, Dorothy Appleby falls under the Sun sign of Capricorn, with Aries as her Ascendant, Gemini as her Moon sign, and Taurus as her Black Moon Lilith sign.
